About this item

Smart summary

Generated by AI

The Comix Lined Journal is a 4-pack set of hardcover notebooks, each with 176 pages of  90gsm premium paper . The notebooks are  5.5 x 8.3 inches  in size, with a college-ruled layout and a durable  1000gsm cover . They feature a  lay-flat design , pen loop, and elastic band. The journals are suitable for note-taking, journaling, and planning, and come in a set of four Morandi colors. The paper is  resistant to ink bleed-through , and the cover has a silky touch with rounded corners.

Quality Journal Notebooks at Good Price

I am completely satisfied with these Comix Lined Journal Notebooks. The colors are a tad more muted than my monitor shows, which makes no difference to me but might to others. The paper thickness is 100GSM as advertised which is important to me. I also like the pocket in the back of the notebooks and the stretchable band to keep them closed. In addition, these notebooks were well priced. I will purchase these again and highly recommend them to others.
